{
  "name": "micro-service",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Monorepo backend containing multiple services: **mono** (.NET 8 gateway), **auth** (.NET 8 auth), **idgen** (Rust gRPC/HTTP ID generator), **auth_rust** (Rust auth), **boardcast** (broadcast), and **app/web/vue** (Vue 3 frontend — client & tenant portals).",
